      "question_pmp": "A project manager is initiating a new compliance project that requires access to a specialized software license. The organization only has a limited number of these licenses, and they are heavily used by other operational teams. What should the project manager's MOST appropriate immediate action be during the Initiating process group regarding this physical resource?",
