        "concepts_to_understand": "Acquire Resources in the Initiating phase involves identifying crucial physical resources and understanding the organizational mechanisms for their acquisition. For constrained resources like software licenses, consulting organizational process assets (OPAs) is paramount. This ensures adherence to internal policies, facilitates efficient resource procurement, and helps determine the feasibility of obtaining necessary licenses early in the project lifecycle, which informs the project's overall viability and initial planning.",
        "additional_notes": "Quick Read: PMI Glossary - Organizational Process Assets (OPAs) - https://www.pmi.org/pmbok-guide-standards/lexicon"
