      "id": "1756635001373",
      "question_pmp": "A project manager is facilitating a new team kick-off meeting. To build team cohesion and to generate initial ideas for team norms and operating procedures, the manager asks each team member to write down their ideas on individual sticky notes. The team then places all the notes on a whiteboard. The next step is for the team to collaboratively organize the notes to identify common patterns and create a concise list of team norms. What is the MOST appropriate technique to use in this situation?",
