      "id": "1756637866058",
      "question_pmp": "The project manager for an e-commerce platform redesign project is reviewing a Logical Data Model with the business stakeholders. A senior stakeholder expresses concern that the model is too abstract and wants to see how it will translate into the actual database. What is the MOST appropriate way for the project manager to address this concern and ensure the stakeholder understands the value of the current model?",
