      "question_pmp": "A project manager is leading a new product development project. The project team is in the forming stage, with low trust and some team members reluctant to share their ideas. The project manager wants to create a sense of unity and psychological safety to foster better collaboration. Which team-building technique would be MOST appropriate to address this specific situation?",
