      "question_pmp": "A project manager is assigned to an existing project that has been experiencing schedule delays and budget overruns. During an initial review, the project manager discovers that the project team is frequently in conflict, lacks a clear understanding of roles and responsibilities, and has poor communication. To address the immediate need for improved collaboration and get the project back on track, what is the FIRST team-building activity the project manager should undertake?",
