        "OPTION_B": "Shorten the stand-up meeting to five minutes to ensure the team is more focused and concise.",
        "OPTION_C": "Change the format of the stand-up from a round-robin update to a 'walk the board' format, where the team focuses on the progress of specific work items.",
        "OPTION_D": "Directly address the disengaged team members in a private meeting and ask them to be more attentive during stand-ups."
