        "option_b_result": "CORRECT - The purpose of a daily stand-up is to identify impediments, not to solve them. The most appropriate action is to politely interrupt the discussion and suggest that the relevant team members meet 'offline' after the stand-up to discuss the issue in detail. This respects the time of everyone in the meeting and ensures the meeting stays on track.",
