        "additional_notes": "This is an easy question that tests the fundamental purpose of a retrospective. The scenario provides a clear description of the meeting's purpose and participants, which points directly to the correct answer. The distractors describe other, distinct agile or traditional project management meetings, making the correct answer obvious.",
