        "concepts_to_understand": "Reinforcement is the final, and often overlooked, stage of the ADKAR® model. It focuses on solidifying the change and preventing a return to the 'old way.' Without proper reinforcement, change is not sustained. This can include visible rewards, celebrating successes, and establishing clear accountability and consequences for not following the new process.",
