        "option_b_result": "INCORRECT - While it's tempting to use momentum for the next change, this would be a mistake. Introducing new changes too soon can disrupt the 'New Beginning' phase, potentially pushing the team back into the 'Neutral Zone' or even sparking renewed resistance. The focus should be on stabilizing the current change first.",
